p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Signature used for the brick Register Health Check
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92: Designed for the lambda functions defined as inputs of the brick Register Health Check, it aims to create custom business logic to check if a service application is healthy or not.
Triggered when the health check start.
Must be triggered by the implementation for the system to consider the application unhealthy.
Must be triggered by the implementation for the system to consider the application healthy.
